{"tid":1326884,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【冷知識】搣Memo紙洗你教","createTime":"2019-07-17T11:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T11:54:04.000Z","uid":281946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e0b10f0e5b839939420352d04e3bbb308d83fac9","tid":1326884,"uid":281946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇post過<br />\n有時見到總有幾張跌左落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔計人為個d<br />\n遇上冇膠紙情況下, 記住呢個方法會痴得貼服d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wv6Xrtc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWv6Xrtc.gif&h=5c453835&s={SIZE}\" /><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HsmXrtK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHsmXrtK.png&h=02790d0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKeep in Mind<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有使用過便利貼的網友們，有沒有遇過一種情形，剛黏上去沒多久，便利貼就自動掉落。荷蘭部落客馬汀(Martin Schapendonk)撰文講解「如何正確撕下便利貼」，美國網友也自拍教學影片，上傳YouTube與大家分享。 <br />\n<br />\n五顏六色的便利貼，是不少人日常生活、上班工作的好幫手，通常大家都會從沒有黏性的底部向上撕開，但撕下的便利貼，常出現捲曲和摺痕，且黏性不持久。馬汀表示，若從有黏性處開始撕，便利貼可保有較多黏性，黏貼較持久。 美國網友威廉（William Turner）也拍攝一支40秒影片示範教學，影片中可見，從黏膠連接處撕下的便利貼，真的比較平整。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20160313/662013.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20160313%2F662013.htm&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5auUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=5be06239\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20160313/662013.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2aa189d844778ed32bbe47e3f80f1e3ab8fe7191","tid":1326884,"uid":82381,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e0b10f0e5b839939420352d04e3bbb308d83fac9","tid":1326884,"uid":281946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇post過<br />\n有時見到總有幾張跌左落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔計人為個d<br />\n遇上冇膠紙情況下, 記住呢個方法會痴